description: 2002 Sea Ray 260 Sundancer. The layout of the boat includes an aft stateroom, full galley to the port side, a full bath with stand up shower to starboard, a dinette forward with seating that converts to V-berth sleeping quarters.This boat is powered with a 5.0 liter E.F.I. Mercury single V/8 motor with a Mercruiser Bravo Three Duo Drive. The full galley includes a propane Kenyon stove, microwave, Norcold 12 or 110 volt refrigerator, sink and above and under counter storage. The head includes a Vacuflush toilet with holding tank, sink and stand up shower. Other features of this boat include dual batteries with built in charger, shore power hot water heater, dock side air conditioning, AM/FM radio with CD changer, 12 volt and 110 lighting as well as 110 volt receptacles throughout. Other items include a remote spot light, anchor with 150' of line, shore power cord as well as docking fenders, lines and life jackets. This Sea Ray is in excellent original condition with only 488 hours showing on the meter. This boat starts easily and handles properly. There are other 260 Sundancers listed that may have more goodies and gadgets. And certainly higher priced models. But it may be difficult to find a cleaner more well kept boat than this one. The hull has no damage and has a nice shine with very few minor scratches from typical use. The interior of this boat is outstanding. There are no stains or soiling to the fabric and the carpet is like new with vinyl carpet protectors throughout. The cockpit features a stern mounted bench seat that folds down for more area, a small removable table with (4) drink holders, a rear facing seat that converts to a lounge and a forward side facing bench seat. There is a single swivel captains seat with stand up or sit to drive positions as well as a tilt steering system. There is a small cockpit sink with pull out shower on the starboard side. The cockpit carpet is also excellent and the vinyl seats are very good with only minor cracking to the aft seat as seen in the photo. The bimini top is new "toast" (tan) colored Sunbrella. There is no damage to the bottom of this Sea Ray and the bottom paint is fresh. Other than perhaps an electronics package based on where you intend to cruise this boat, this Sea Ray is ready to drop in the water and enjoy. The trailer that is pictured with the boat is NOT INCLUDED with the sale. The boat is stored indoors in Windsor, Pennsylvania which is close to York, Lancaster and Harrisburg, Pa. as well as Baltimore, Maryland. I encourage all serious buyers to call show contact info for more information or to make an appointment to see this boat. All emails, text and spam will be ignored. If it is listed, it is available.
title: 2002 Sea Ray 260 Sundancer
